  english: 'The objective of the game is to add 21 with the cards in your hand, or
    to get as close as possible without going overboard. Initially you will receive
    two cards, and you can request as many as you need by clicking on the "Continue"
    button. When you are satisfied with the cards in your hand, press "Stand Up".


    Now
    the computer''s turn will begin. He will receive cards until he draws a number
    greater than 21 (you win the game), he draws a number greater than yours and
    not greater than 21 (you lose the game), or he draws a number equal to yours
    and decides not to continue playing (you draw) .


    If your two starting cards
    add up to 21, you automatically win the game.


    All the cards add their value
    except J, Q and K (add 10 points) and A (add one point or 11 points, the higher
    score prevailing as long as it is not higher than 21).'
  spanish: "El objetivo del juego es sumar 21 con las cartas de tu mano, o acercarse
    lo m\xE1ximo posible sin llegar a pasarse. Inicialmente recibir\xE1s dos cartas,
    y podr\xE1s pedir cuantas necesites pulsando en el bot\xF3n \"Continuar\". Cuando
    est\xE9s conforme con las cartas en tu mano, pulsa \"Plantarse\".\r\n\r\nAhora
    comenzar\xE1 el turno del ordenador. Recibir\xE1 cartas hasta que saque un n\xFAmero
    superior a 21 (ganas la partida), saque un n\xFAmero superior al tuyo y no superior
    a 21 (pierdes la partida), o saque un n\xFAmero igual al tuyo y decida no seguir
    jugando (empatas la partida).\r\n\r\nSi tus dos cartas iniciales suman 21, ganas
    autom\xE1ticamente la partida.\r\n\r\nTodas las cartas suman su valor salvo J,
    Q y K (suman 10 puntos) y A (suma un punto o 11 puntos, prevaleciendo la puntuaci\xF3n
    superior siempre que no sea superior a 21)."
